r of Tunare <BR>Cousin of Fall<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udarkhawkx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DarkhawkX</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com:80/darkhawkx/test1.gif x=29 y=38 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/3/01 3:17:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RZ</span><hr size=1> I know what you mean as I hail from the most politicaly distraught server of them all, Rallos Zek.<br><br>Baeandar would probably agree with me that it's worth the strife. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udondorholystorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DondorHolystorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/16/01 9:24:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RZ</span><hr size=1> I feel your pain.<br><br>You chose PvP on your own accord.<br><br>I'm sorry you consider Non-PvP players inferior to PvP, &quot;Carebear&quot; and the like comments lead me to believe this.<br><br>I chose Non-PvP for the simple reason, I don't like PvP.  It's not my cup of tea.  I shoot other people with paintballs when I want to PvP.  I play the game for enjoyment.  Looking over my shoulder ever second of my game time just does not appeal to me.<br><br>Because I am on a Blue Server doesn't make me any less of a paladin than you are, nor does it lessen the accomplishment of me finishing my epic.  <br><br>Hope you accomplish your epic one day.  You will enjoy it. <p>"Death smiles at us all, all a man can do is smile back."<a href="http://www.mithrilweb.com//"target="web"><img src="http://www.mithrilweb.com/images/sigs/donsassig.jpg" border="0"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usetthadelight.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Settha Delight</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/21/01 8:21:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RZ</span><hr size=1> Thats the reason I didnt pick PVP, cause of people that would ruin the game for me and others.<br><br>I don't find PVP appealing to me, and I dont see myself as a 'less' pally because of it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><img src=http://setthapics.freewebspace.com/images/setthacard.jpg>Settha Delight55th LevelThe Seventh Hammer</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulalehn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lalehn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/21/01 8:10:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: RZ</span><hr size=1> I hail from Vallon Zek...<br><br>I dont think anyone is inferior for the server that they play on, everyone has their preferences.  However...<br><br>It is a significantly greater accomplishment for a pally to get his epic on a PvP server than on a carebear server, for the simple reason that there are more obstacles to overcome.  I'm currently 49, and i spent the last two levels soloing in Sol B, against the doggies.  It's a disputed zone, and I never know whether i will find friend or foe.  So i suck it in, wear a mix of ac/resist gear and hold my ground.  The only players that can oust me one on one are either fungi twinks, or an SK with about 5-6 levels on me, and I'm NOT a twink.  I just know how to trade=P.  Shout outs to all the peeps that find carebear too boring <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>-Lalehn the Bulletproof <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>i r ubr /growl<br><br>P.S.  Caster's LOVE it when you zone dance with em.  Nothing like jousting them for 100+ dmg then zoning b4 their cast goes thru muhahahaha <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulalehn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lalehn</A> at: 12/21/01 8:12:58 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion.showMessage?topicID=159.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion.showMessage?topicID=176.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=154.topic&index=4><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td>